text: Agirtamak () is a rural locality (a selo) in Tyumenyakovsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 610 as of 2010. There are 10 streets. == Geography == It is located 5 km from Tuymazy, 6 km from Tyumenyak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Agirtamak
